    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just so tired of trying. like, every single day is just this massive effort to pretend i'm normal just so people dont look at me weird. it feels like i'm playing a character in a movie and i'm the only one who hasn't read the script. i dont think i'll ever actually belong anywhere.",
